<h1>Help</h1>
<p>
  If you have forgotten your password, please post your concerns on the wall for
  <a href="www.facebook.com">PolyWho</a>'s
  Facebook page.
  <br>
  <br>
  <B>How to get a profile picture:</b>
  <br>
  Go to the settings tab and scroll to the bottom and click on change.  It will bring you to www.gravatar.com.  It is a free service.  Just provide your <i><b>Cal Poly Email Address</b></i>, a password, and a photo!
 
</p>
